Here, type 1 (jdbc-odbc bridge) driver is used as the driver.
Before 1.6, this driver was required to be loaded manually. But since 1.6 and till 1.8, 
JVM (Sun) provided this driver with preloaded internally. Since 1.8, this driver is completely removed.

Oracle provides OracleDriver class for loading the driver internally using oracle provided ojdbc jar.

Connections must be closed or else after a certain limit, new connection to database would not be possible.